;; BIND zone file — merchmaxxing.xyz → GitHub Pages (oldmanstillcan/merchmaxxing)
;; Import at Cloudflare: DNS → Records → Import and Export → Import DNS records
;; IMPORTANT: leave "Proxy imported DNS records" UNCHECKED (records must be DNS-only
;; until GitHub issues the SSL cert).
$ORIGIN merchmaxxing.xyz.
$TTL 300

@    IN  A      185.199.108.153
@    IN  A      185.199.109.153
@    IN  A      185.199.110.153
@    IN  A      185.199.111.153

www  IN  CNAME  oldmanstillcan.github.io.
